**Done:** I added a built-in `weather` skill under `pulsar-agentic\src\main\resources\skills\weather` so it auto-loads with the other bundled skills. It includes a new `SKILL.md` and a Python script, `scripts\get_weather.py`, that uses Open-Meteo geocoding + forecast APIs to return current conditions and a structured 7-day forecast JSON for a named location, with optional country-code disambiguation.

I also updated `pulsar-agentic\src\main\resources\skills\README.md` to list the skill, and extended the skill tests in `SkillBootstrapIntegrationTest.kt` and `SkillDefinitionLoaderTest.kt` so `weather` is explicitly discovered, auto-registered, and parsed with its metadata and parameters.


